metadata.name: SOPHIE
metadata.description:
This piece is part of my newest collection-
"50 /50 SPLIT" 
For many years of doing photography i've worked with so many models and creatives in the industry that have put in hours of work of creating for web2-
but now that we're headed into web3 i'm starting to release a few my pieces as NFTs and educating + getting friends involved by giving them 50% of anything that they're involved in gets minted/sold

If a stylist/makeup artist etc-is ever involved they will also be given a % of the sold NFTs as well

I believe this is the future of collaborations for creatives.
